# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .gitignore — TaskFlow Task Management System
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# WHAT IS .gitignore?
# ────────────────────
# Tells Git which files to NEVER commit to the repository.
# Critical for:
#   ✓ Keeping secrets out of GitHub (passwords, API keys)
#   ✓ Excluding compiled files (regenerated on every build)
#   ✓ Excluding OS/IDE junk files

# ════════════════════
# ⚠️  SECRETS — NEVER COMMIT THESE
# ════════════════════
.env
.env.local
.env.production
.env.staging
azure-credentials.json
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
*.p12
secrets/

# ════════════════════
# .NET / ASP.NET Core
# ════════════════════
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/publish/
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
*.DotSettings.user

# EF Core migration snapshots (commit migrations, not snapshots)
# **/Migrations/

# Test results
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
*.trx
*.coveragexml
*.cobertura.xml

# ════════════════════
# Node.js / React
# ════════════════════
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Vite build output
frontend/dist/
frontend/build/
frontend/.vite/

# ════════════════════
# Docker
# ════════════════════
# Don't ignore docker-compose files — they're project config
# But ignore any override files with real passwords
docker-compose.override.yml

# ════════════════════
# Logs
# ════════════════════
logs/
*.log
backend/src/TaskFlow.API/logs/

# ════════════════════
# IDE — Visual Studio Code
# ════════════════════
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

# ════════════════════
# IDE — JetBrains (Rider)
# ════════════════════
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws

# ════════════════════
# Operating System
# ════════════════════
# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# Linux
*~

# ════════════════════
# Azure
# ════════════════════
.azure/
PublishProfiles/
*.pubxml
*.pubxml.user

# ════════════════════
# Certificates (dev SSL)
# ════════════════════
*.crt
*.cer
https/
